33:45.620 --> 33:49.880
(METALLIC RINGING)

33:49.880 --> 33:51.710
Sorry to interrupt the fun,

33:51.710 --> 33:53.500
but Her Highness is here.

33:55.620 --> 33:56.920
It's time to get
what we came for.

33:58.710 --> 33:59.960
Yes, it is.

33:59.960 --> 34:01.880
